	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Does frequent writes/reads of battery backed RAM wear out anything?  Use more juice?
<br />
<br />Do flash carts suffer any wear from emulated battery RAM access?  I mean, they shouldn't immediately write back to flash, right?

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


	<hr width="85%" />

